reviews.text:
This is a great base recipe. I mixed it and it was good, but personally found it lacking in a few areas. Here are the changes that I have made. &#xD;
Good as a shake &amp; vape, but it's best after a 3 day steep.&#xD;
60vg / 40pg (Now that it's gotten hotter outside I'm mixing this at 70vg / 30pg and its still delicious.)&#xD;
5% FLV Cinnamon Crunch&#xD;
3.25% FLV Cream&#xD;
0.50% FLV Milk&#xD;
2.5% CAP Cereal 27&#xD;
0.25% CAP Fuji Apple (Turns it into an apple cinnamon toast crunch, can be left out for that original cinnamon toast crunch flavor.)&#xD;
0.50% CAP Super Sweet
